metadata.name: DreamVapours I
metadata.description:
“DreamVapours I”

First in a series of images psychonavigating obscure, liminal landscapes and vistas. These are the images which leak through the thin membrane that separates us from our dreams. 

Resolution 4961x7440 – JPEG - 1/1
Digital photo taken with Canon 60D

Included with the 1st purchase is a high quality PHYSICAL PRINT. To receive it, contact me & provide proof of purchase. To redeem please read the [FAQ:]( https://tinyurl.com/32zr29we)
